## Import

Lifecycle configurations can be imported using the bucket name:

```shell
terraform import minio_s3_bucket_lifecycle.example my-bucket
```

## Relationship with `minio_ilm_policy`

Both `minio_s3_bucket_lifecycle` and `minio_ilm_policy` manage the same underlying
S3 bucket lifecycle configuration. **Do not configure both resources for the same
bucket** — they will fight each other on every plan. New configurations should
prefer `minio_s3_bucket_lifecycle`, which mirrors the AWS provider schema
(`aws_s3_bucket_lifecycle_configuration`).
